description: AegirBio AB engages in the development and commercialization of drug monitoring tests. The company is headquartered in Lund, Skane and currently employs 1 full-time employees. The company went IPO on 2020-06-26. The firm's tests for optimized dosage of biological drugs focused on diseases in neurology, autoimmune diseases and cancer.
